  _characterSheet: {fileID: 0}
  _missions:
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: forgeKnife
    Title: Joren's Forge
    Summary: Forge Wren a proper curved foraging knife.
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: cottagesReopen
    Title: Two Boards Come Down
    Summary: Make hinges for the first repaired cottages.
  _quotes:
  - Text: Pretty costs extra and cuts worse.
    Context: Taking Wren's knife commission.
  - Text: Come back tomorrow. And don't tell anyone you commissioned it like charity.
    Context: Protecting his pride after accepting the work.
  - Text: Old nails. Rotten frame. No one respects hinges until they fail.
    Context: Repairing the cottage shutters.
